{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465640/extras/hollowMineSteamStoreDescCombat.gif?t=1739785749\" />Hollow Mine is a climatic fast paced roguelike hack-and-slash dungeon crawler game with crafting and mining elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become a <strong>hero</strong> who was <strong>assigned with a task</strong>. Go deep into the mine and <strong>destroy evil artifact</strong>.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465640/extras/hollowMineSteamStoreDescMining.gif?t=1739785749\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive yourself into this challenging adventure inside a Hollow Mine. Fight challenging bosses and various enemies. Explore this exciting game with lots of weapons, magic, abilities and classes. Every session brings a new adventure, discover new and fun ways to deal with the enemies each time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465640/extras/hollowMineSteamStoreDescAction.gif?t=1739785749\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Demo Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in action-packed combat with a variety of weapons. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dig for resources to craft weapons, spells, and potions. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore [randomly generated, destructible rooms. Access two biomes from total of five.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Level up and pick from 30 unique abilities. 30 from more than 50 abilities available. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the environment creatively to defeat enemies. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight unique enemies and bosses in two first biomes of five total. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy 20-minute demo play session.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find loot like weapons, magic scrolls, jewelry, and herbs in chests. Reduced pool of items for demo. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pick from multiple character classes with different play styles. Restricted characters in demo. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take on fun challenges in various rooms. Reduced number of rooms in demo. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience hand-crafted pixel art world. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect gold to buy or sell items from NPCs. Restricted number of NPC's and dialogs in demo. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Visit Hollow Mine Main Store Page for full list of features available after release</p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465640/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739785749","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465640/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1739785749","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465640/fcf86461dc1cc44460058a0c13cf996492cc5a1b/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739785749","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465640/fcf86461dc1cc44460058a0c13cf996492cc5a1b/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739785749","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465640/extras/hollowMineSteamStoreDescCombat.gif?t=1739785749\" />Hollow Mine is a climatic fast paced roguelike hack-and-slash dungeon crawler game with crafting and mining elements. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become a <strong>hero</strong> who was <strong>assigned with a task</strong>. Go deep into the mine and <strong>destroy evil artifact</strong>.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465640/extras/hollowMineSteamStoreDescMining.gif?t=1739785749\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dive yourself into this challenging adventure inside a Hollow Mine. Fight challenging bosses and various enemies. Explore this exciting game with lots of weapons, magic, abilities and classes. Every session brings a new adventure, discover new and fun ways to deal with the enemies each time. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465640/extras/hollowMineSteamStoreDescAction.gif?t=1739785749\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Demo Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Engage in action-packed combat with a variety of weapons. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dig for resources to craft weapons, spells, and potions. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore [randomly generated, destructible rooms. Access two biomes from total of five.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Level up and pick from 30 unique abilities. 30 from more than 50 abilities available. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use the environment creatively to defeat enemies. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Fight unique enemies and bosses in two first biomes of five total. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy 20-minute demo play session.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Find loot like weapons, magic scrolls, jewelry, and herbs in chests. Reduced pool of items for demo. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pick from multiple character classes with different play styles. Restricted characters in demo. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take on fun challenges in various rooms. Reduced number of rooms in demo. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience hand-crafted pixel art world. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect gold to buy or sell items from NPCs. Restricted number of NPC's and dialogs in demo. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Visit Hollow Mine Main Store Page for full list of features available after release</p></li></ul>","developers":["Micha\u0142 Parysz"],"fullgame":{"appid":"2465060","name":"Hollow Mine"},"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3465640/header.jpg?t=1739785749","is_free":true,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257099196,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257099196/movie480.mp4?t=1739784846","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257099196/movie_max.mp4?t=1739784846"},"name":"Hollow Mine Gameplay Trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257099196/320b5c25b84f3113ee49b045b855dbd6f395fb64/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1739784846","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257099196/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1739784846","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257099196/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1739784846"}}],"name":"Hollow Mine Demo","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Requires a 64-bit processor and operating system<br></li><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> 1.2Ghz+<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 1024 MB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> 512MB<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 512 MB available space</li></ul>","recommend